data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully remodeled 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom bungalow in Williamsburg—a very desirable Orlando location! The updated move-in ready home is located on a premium lot with NO rear neighbors. The home’s interior has been transformed with great attention to detail. The spacious open kitchen “POPS” with new throughout--backsplash, granite, cabinets, pantry, flooring, appliances, larger island & more counter space making this kitchen a chef’s dream come true. The spacious Family/Dining Room has new Bamboo flooring, crown molding, recessed lighting & a wood burning fireplace. Bedrooms 1 & 2 have new flooring plus crown molding. The 2nd bathroom has been tastefully remodeled. The Master Bedroom can easily accommodate a King size-bed plus additional furnishings. The ensuite bath is new from top to bottom--walk in shower, vanity, backlit mirror-total spa relaxation. The bonus room located at the rear of the home is perfect for a 4th bedroom, media room, study area—the perfect “extra” space.  The screened area located off the Living/Dining room is a wonderful relaxing space. Want more? The home has ALL new double pane windows, gutters, soffits, down spouts, new flat roof (rear), HVAC, duct work & electrical panel. The HOA covers lawn maintenance plus the neighborhood amenities include pool, tennis court & clubhouse. Conveniently located to I-4, 528, 417. Downtown Orlando, OIA, Parks & shopping.
